result.formatted_address: 42 Mody Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: Spring Deer

reviews.text:
I  have been going to Spring Deer for over 40 (forty) years and have always loved the experience. Each visit though i always order whole Peking Duck.  It always is  best. At the end I get the duck soup.
The pancakes are always light and flavorful especially after Hoisin sauce and scallions. The duck is moist, flavorful and smoked to perfection.   i get excited just thinking about it!  
Every other restaurant that I try the Peking  Duck does not measure up.  
So I stick with the best and am never disappointed. I plan my Hong Kong trips around visiting Spring Deer. But I must try other items on their menu next time.  Maybe next time I will order a half duck and venture out and ask what they suggest to try.  I am sure that it will be great and tasty.

We came here around 6.15 PM without a reservation. Although it was fully booked we were given a table and promptly served. The staff was attentive and very sweet. It is a very busy restaurant but we were served promptly. We had the Peking duck which was outstanding and compared to other places that served the same dish at inferior quality the price here was OK. I highly recommend making an advanced reservation to avoid disappointment.

The peking duck seemed good to me. The place doesn't seem that clean and the service was very attentive. Almost instant reactions when you're finished with something.

The picked vegetables wasn't free.

Here is posted on tourist guide book therefore always crowded but in reality taste is just so so. Beijing duck is famous that is bit oily and skin is not well cooked. If you like this type of duck, it is fine.

Great traditional Chinese restaurant. Will try and squeeze you in even without a reservation. Of course the duck is superb. But everything else is too. Great old school service where nothing is too much trouble.  A must if you are in Tsim Sha Tsui

result.name: 鹿鳴春

reviews.text: 古老方法美食🤗🤗🤗
網民上周六(27日)發起「光復元朗」活動，引起一連串警民衝突。網上多個討論區及Facebook專頁轉載一名疑似於瑪嘉烈醫院擔任骨科顧問醫生的貼文，引起廣泛熱議，貼文指若有斷手斷腳的人入院，就「一個不留，大大力打」，疑語帶相關。一眾網民認為有關醫生言論帶有恐嚇成分，足以令市民及示威者不敢求醫，擬集體向醫管局等部門投訴。

北京ダックを食べるために行きました。
オープン時間に行くと並ばずに入れました。
カリッとした皮とジューシーな身ときゅうりを餃子の皮みたなので包んで、五平餅のタレのような味のタレをつけて頂きます。
量がありましたがペロッといけました。
お勧めです。
